            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker in St. Martin's-lane. I have a guitar, which was pawned for 1l. 10s., but not by the prisoner - this is the duplicate.</p>
               <p>PROSECUTOR. This is one he gave me.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He sold me the three instruments before two witnesses.</p>
